    \index{hal \textit{(package)}!hal.maths \textit{(package)}!hal.maths.crypt \textit{(module)}|(}
\section{Module hal.maths.crypt}

    \label{hal:maths:crypt}
\begin{alltt}
Perform fast hash, encryption and calculations related to cryptography. 
\end{alltt}
